data.description: Discover your dream home in this quiet neighborhood--a well cared for 4 level split residence. Three spacious bedrooms and two full upgraded bathrooms. Step into a newer kitchen, laminate countertops and updated, white cabinets. Hardwood flooring, Newer hot water tank, newer widows, adding further appeal to this remarkable home. Seconds to DCSC. MCE hospital and 270, minutes to Downtown Columbus and Air Port. Short drive to Amazon and Limited! it does not get much better! Schedule your private tour today!! Sale of property is contingent upon seller finding and closing on a suitable home.
